result.name: Beijing Dumpling Restaurant

reviews.text: Easy to get a seat here, I will be back again.

This northern style Chinese dumpling place has been at the bus terminal for years.

Serve very good dumplings, noodles, soy milk, hot and sour soup etc.  Inexpensive.
Mostly locals and Chinese speaking.
多年老店平均食物也好,多自己制作食材'價錢又合理支持小店
菜飯不熱牛肉餅不熱 衛生環境不好 味道不錯 交通方便 響正元朗西站 搭巴士容易
每次經過也要進去食一碗鳳爪水餃麵
